ationship between both measurement\ntechniques. All in all, PEA in combination with TSDC turns out to be a useful\ntechnique in the study of thermally poled electrets, either in the study of\nrelaxations or of external charge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Mar 2021 17:20:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 17:01:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2022 09:48:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-09"}
