g from the deep RNN-based controllers is 60% less than\nthe variance of the risk-averse baseline.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Mar 2021 19:15:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Aug 2021 13:38:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-20"}
