onfiguration approach\nimproves the compression ratio of up to 73% on the tested datasets with the\nsame post-analysis distortion with only 1% performance overhead.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 00:51:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Apr 2021 16:07:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 22:59:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-22"}
