ER of 30.73% and 32.45% on the test sets of\nmultilingual and code-switching subtasks, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 03:37:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-21"}
