perconductivity appears to be more robust than expected from\nIsing protection alone. Our data can be explained by the above-mentioned ESTPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 08:19:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 14:28:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-03"}
