ear $k_\\text{F}$, from which the TL liquid interaction\nparameter $K_{\\rho}$ is calculated. The value of the TL parameter is found to\nbe in agreement with that of a single wire for large separation between the two\nwires.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 14:41:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Jun 2021 10:35:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
