 topography primarily\ndrives the eddy activity throughout the Martian year, and that although latent\nheat release can produce an annular vortex, it has a relatively minor effect on\nvortex variability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 15:03:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2021 11:01:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 08:38:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-30"}
