ive crops, while\nproviding LPF comparable to the standard North-South faced solar farms.\nAdditional benefits include reduced soiling and ease of movement of large-scale\ncombine-harvester and other farming equipment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 15:38:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-02"}
